
Introduction to Prompt Techniques – Answers
Exercise 1: Identify the Prompt Technique
Prompt:
"Summarize the following paragraph in one sentence."
Answer: Zero-Shot Prompting
Explanation:
This is an example of Zero-Shot Prompting because the AI is asked to perform the task directly without being given any examples beforehand.
