Exercise 3: Choose the Correct Technique
Scenario:
You want the AI to follow the same writing style every time while generating responses.
Answer: Few-Shot Prompting
Justification:
Few-Shot Prompting is the best choice because providing multiple examples helps the AI recognize patterns and maintain a consistent writing style across different outputs.
